[The enterovirus (or enteroviruses) involved in this outbreak is not specifically stated and HFMD can be caused by a variety of viruses. Cases in Southeast Asia in recent years have been primarily caused by enterovirus 71 (EV71), which has caused severe complications in some children. - Mod.LL

